Tools 
pfanne 
schuessel
teller

Ingredients 
ei 2 PIECE 
salz 1 TEESPOON
oel 1 TABLESPOON

Instructions
Use pfanne
Apply oel
Cook on HOT temperature until "pfanne ist heiß genug"
Use schuessel
Apply ei
Apply oel
Blend until "alles gut verrührt"
Transfer from schuessel to pfanne
Cook on MEDIUM temperature for 10 MINUTES
Transfer from pfanne to teller

